These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Birthday: march, april, october, july
Transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. Birthday:july is on the left of Birthday:march##1
2. Birthday:march is on the right of Birthday:july##1
3. Transport:car is on the far left or far right##3
4. Birthday:october is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Transport:roller is between Transport:car and Transport:motorbike##2
6. Birthday:july == Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | july | march     | october | april |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
House: tower, art-deco, cape-cod, modern
Transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. House:art-deco is on the left of Transport:helicopter##1
2. Transport:trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. House:modern is on the left of Transport:trike##1
4. Transport:trike is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1
5. House:cape-cod is on the far right##1
6. Transport:bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| House   | tower | art-deco    | modern     | cape-cod  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

