.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
Music-Genre: house, jazz, pop, rock
Flower: poppy, sunflower, begonia, iris
1. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Music-Genre:jazz##3
2. Music-Genre:jazz is on the far left##1
3. Flower:begonia is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1
4. Flower:poppy is on the left or right of Music-Genre:house##3
5. Flower:begonia is on the right of Music-Genre:pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Flower           | sunflower | iris | begonia | poppy  |

