.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
City: boston, nizza, rome, new-york
Nationality: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. Nationality:indian is on the left of City:rome##1
2. City:new-york is between City:boston and Nationality:egyptian##2
3. City:new-york is on the left or right of City:rome##3
4. Nationality:egyptian is on the left or right of Nationality:indian##3
5. City:boston is on the right of City:nizza##1
6. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| City         | nizza | boston | new-york | rome  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

